<pre><code class=3D"language-python hljs"><span class=3D"hljs-function"><sp=
an class=3D"hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class=3D"hljs-title">bisection</=
span><span class=3D"hljs-params">(f,a,b,N)</span>:</span>
    <span class=3D"hljs-string">'''Approximate solution of f(x)=3D0 on inte=
rval [a,b] by bisection method.

