r some
        midpoint m_n =3D (a_n + b_n)/2, then the function returns this solu=
tion.
        If all signs of values f(a_n), f(b_n) and f(m_n) are the same at an=
y
        iteration, the bisection method fails and return None.

    Examples
    --------
