<pre><code class=3D"language-python hljs">f =3D <span class=3D"hljs-keyword=
">lambda</span> x: x**<span class=3D"hljs-number">2</span> - x - <span clas=
s=3D"hljs-number">1</span>
approx_phi =3D bisection(f,<span class=3D"hljs-number">1</span>,<span class=
=3D"hljs-number">2</span>,<span class=3D"hljs-number">25</span>)
print(approx_phi)
</code></pre>
<pre><code class=3D"nohighlight">1.618033990263939
</code></pre>
<p>The absolute error is guaranteed to be less than <span class=3D"MathJax_=
