<p>Let's verify the absolute error is then than this error bound:</p>
<pre><code class=3D"language-python hljs">abs( (<span class=3D"hljs-number"=
>1</span> + <span class=3D"hljs-number">5</span>**<span class=3D"hljs-numbe=
r">0.5</span>)/<span class=3D"hljs-number">2</span> - approx_phi) &lt; erro=
r_bound
</code></pre>
<pre><code class=3D"nohighlight">True
</code></pre>
